OL,3,CIllegal puppy seller from Rugeley
OL,4,Chanded suspended jail sentence
OL,6,FA man from Rugeley has been sentenced
OL,7,Ffor fraudulently selling puppies to
OL,8,Fpeople across the UK.
OL,10,FRichard Butler, 57, from Springfield
OL,11,FFarm in Rugeley, was handed a 21 month
OL,12,Fsuspended sentence at Stafford Crown
OL,13,FCourt.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to three offences of
OL,16,Ffraud and one offence of making
OL,17,Farticles for use in fraud.
