OL,6,FButler's sentence was suspended for
OL,7,Ftwo years and he has been ordered to
OL,8,Fcomplete 200 hours of community
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FThe court heard how Butler had been
OL,12,Frefused a license to sell dogs due to
OL,13,Fpoor conditions and hygiene practices
OL,14,Fat his farm.
OL,16,FHowever, between October 2015 and May
OL,17,F2018 Butler sold around five hundred
OL,18,Fpuppies for #500 each - With trading
OL,19,Fstandards estimating his fraudulent
OL,20,Factivities earned him around a quarter
OL,21,Fof a million pounds.
