OL,6,FButler selected popular breeds of dogs
OL,7,Fto advertise and falsely claimed the
OL,8,Fpuppies from from a little from his
OL,9,Ffamily dog.
OL,11,FIn reality he had bought the dogs from
OL,12,Fa variety of sources, created fake
OL,13,Fpedigree certificates and fake
OL,14,Fvaccination records.
OL,16,FMany of the puppies Butler sold were
OL,17,Fsuffering from genetic conditions and
OL,18,Fparvo virus - meaning some of the
OL,19,Fpuppies died within a short time of
OL,20,Fbeing sold.
