OL,6,FStaffordshire Country Council's
OL,7,FTrading Standards team, who prosecuted
OL,8,FButler, first visited the farm in May
OL,9,F2018 following a complaint from a
OL,10,Fmember of the public.
OL,12,FVictoria Wilson, Cabinet Member with
OL,13,Fresponsibility for Trading Standards
OL,14,Fat Staffordshire County Council, urged
OL,15,Fanyone who has suspicions when buying
OL,16,Fa puppy to contact the authorities.
OL,18,FShe said: "Demand for fashionable
OL,19,Fbreeds of puppies is always high, so
OL,20,Fit can be a very lucrative business.
